- Increased max_tokens from 256 to 1024
- Increased default n from 30 to 200
- Added metadata mismatch detection (num_questions + max_tokens)
- Added baseline_accuracy=0 infrastructure error check
- Tiered profiling strategy: probe-driven Tier 0 (nsys node) / Tier 1 (torch.profiler Chrome traces) / Tier 2 (nsys graph enrichment)
- New reference: torch-profiler-guide.md (Chrome trace parsing, multi-rank analysis, kernel chains, BW estimation, occupancy caveats)
